790:16771.name: .Button Group Variants
790:16771.description:
Button Group

A button group bunches toggleable actions together.
Button groups act like radios.

We recommend using them when there are less than 4 actions for text button groups.

When using as an icon only button group use as many as necessary and always pair with a tootip text on hover.
